OL,3,CTeacher ballot on strike action to
OL,4,Copen over contact time dispute
OL,6,FMembers of Scotland's largest teaching
OL,7,Funion are being urged to back strike
OL,8,Faction over a dispute on class contact
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FThe SNP pledged in its manifesto ahead
OL,12,Fof the 2021 election to reduce contact
OL,13,Ftime to 21 hours per week, but EIS
OL,14,Fgeneral secretary Andrea Bradley said
OL,15,Fthe Government has "delivered
OL,16,Fabsolutely nothing".
