OL,3,CTeacher ballot on strike action to
OL,4,Copen over contact time dispute
OL,6,FMembers will be able to vote from
OL,7,FWednesday until January 14 on
OL,8,Fpotential action as a result, with the
OL,9,Funion's leadership pushing for
OL,10,Fteachers to back both strike action
OL,11,Fand action short of a strike.
OL,13,FThe Scottish Government said it is
OL,14,F"disappointed" the ballot has been
OL,15,Fopened.
OL,17,FAny action would be likely to be taken
OL,18,Fahead of next year's Holyrood election
OL,19,Fand could damage the prospects of the
OL,20,FSNP if a resolution is not reached.
