OL,3,CTeacher ballot on strike action to
OL,4,Copen over contact time dispute
OL,6,F"In opening this ballot, we are
OL,7,Freminding the Scottish Government and
OL,8,FCosla that it is essential that they
OL,9,Fkeep their promises to Scottish
OL,10,Feducation, Scotland's teachers and
OL,11,FScotland's learners," Ms Bradley said.
OL,13,F"It is simply not acceptable for
OL,14,Fnational or local politicians to be
OL,15,Felected on the promise of improving
OL,16,Feducation, in this case by tackling
OL,17,Fteacher workload and employing more
OL,18,Fteachers, then failing to deliver upon
OL,19,Fthose promises, particularly when
OL,20,Fissues around teacher workload and
OL,21,Fprecarity of employment are so serious.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]uD@AOU
