OL,3,CTeacher ballot on strike action to
OL,4,Copen over contact time dispute
OL,6,F"This ballot is a chance for
OL,7,FScotland's teachers to show both their
OL,8,Femployers and the Scottish Government
OL,9,Ftheir strength of feeling, and to
OL,10,Fcompel them to work constructively
OL,11,Ftogether and act on teacher workload.
OL,13,F"I would urge all eligible EIS members
OL,14,Fto look out for their ballot paper
OL,15,Farriving in the post, and to cast
OL,16,Ftheir vote in this hugely important
OL,17,Fballot.
