OL,3,CTeacher ballot on strike action to
OL,4,Copen over contact time dispute
OL,6,F"The EIS executive strongly recommends
OL,7,Fto members that they should vote yes
OL,8,Fto strike action and yes to action
OL,9,Fshort of strike.
OL,11,F"We must send the type of strong and
OL,12,Funited message that is impossible for
OL,13,Fthe politicians to ignore."
OL,15,FThe patience of both teachers and the
OL,16,Funion, Ms Bradley added, was "at an
OL,17,Fend on this issue".
