OL,6,FA spokesman for the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment said: "Ministers have been
OL,8,Fclear that reducing class contact will
OL,9,Fhelp support the time and space
OL,10,Fnecessary for teachers, to allow them
OL,11,Fto drive improvement and reform in our
OL,12,Fschools and improve outcomes for their
OL,13,Fpupils.
OL,15,F"We are committed to working with
OL,16,Fteaching unions and Cosla to agree our
OL,17,Fapproach to delivering a reduction in
OL,18,Fclass contact time at pace.
